headline: Lennar Corporation's First Quarter Earnings Conference Call to be Broadcast Live on the Internet
summary: Lennar Corporation (NYSE: LEN and LEN.B), one of the nation's largest homebuilders, announced today that the Company will release earnings for the first quarter ended February 28, 2025 after the market closes on March 20, 2025. Additionally, the Company will hold a conference call on March 21, 2025 at 11:00 a.m. Eastern Time.
